paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import DoubleType, StringType, StructType, StructField


udf_dhm = udf(lambda s: s[:-3])
udf_double = udf(lambda s: float(s), DoubleType())

th = spark.read.option("header", "false")\
               .option("sep", ",")\
               .schema(StructType([
                   StructField('datetime', StringType(), True),
                   StructField('temp', DoubleType(), True),
                   StructField('humi', DoubleType(), True)
               ]))\
               .csv('file:///home/witlab/temphumi_20190413.csv')

th.show()
th2 = th.withColumn('datetime', udf_dhm('datetime'))\
        .withColumn('temp', udf_double('temp'))\
        .withColumn('humi', udf_double('humi'))\
        .groupby('datetime').avg('temp', 'humi')\
        .sort('datetime')
th2.show()

%pyspark

udf_dnt2dt = udf(lambda d, t: d + ' ' + t)
udf_dts2dt = udf(lambda d: d[:-3])

uv = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/uv_srs.parquet')\
          .withColumn('datetime', udf_dnt2dt('date', 'time'))\
          .select('datetime', 'uvb', 'uvi')
wt = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///weather/witlab/wtob.parquet')\
          .withColumn('datetime', udf_dts2dt('datetime'))\
          .select('datetime', 'tempout', 'humout','uvindex')

uv.sort(uv.datetime.desc()).show()

uvthwt = uv.join(th, 'datetime')
uvthwt.show()
uvthwt.createOrReplaceTempView('uvthwt')

%pyspark
temphumi = spark.read.format('jdbc').options(
        url='jdbc:mysql://localhost/chamber_monitor',
        driver='com.mysql.jdbc.Driver',
        dbtable='temphumi', user='chamberman', password='defacto8*'
    ).load()
    
temphumi.show()

%pyspark

from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import StringType

udf_minute = udf(lambda s: s.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M'), StringType())

temphumi.printSchema()

th = temphumi.withColumn('datetime', udf_minute(temphumi.datetime))
th.show()

%pyspark

from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import StringType

udf_minute = udf(lambda s: s.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M'), StringType())
udf_dt = udf(lambda d, t: d + ' ' + t)

nt = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/nt_srs.parquet')
uv = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/uv_srs.parquet')
df_ntuv = nt.join(uv, ['date', 'time']).withColumn('datetime', udf_dt('date', 'time'))\
            .select('datetime', 'illum', 'cct', 'uvb', 'euvb', 'uvi')
df_ntuv.show()
